title: Fouad Ali
text: Fouad Ali (born 6 March 1936) is an Egyptian <a href="amateur%20wrestling">wrestler</a>. He competed in the <a href="Wrestling%20at%20the%201964%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20Greco-Roman%20flyweight">men's Greco-Roman flyweight</a> at the <a href="1964%20Summer%20Olympics">1964 Summer Olympics</a>.
